      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why i'm talking to you. everything just feels... heavy. like i've spent 6 years pouring every single thing i am into this research and now that the funding is gone and the lab is shutting down, i realize there’s nothing actually left of me. i'm just so tired of trying to fight for a life that doesn't even want me anymore. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to rest so badly.",
