      "content": "it feels like more than just a heavy feeling though. like it's permanent. if i keep trying to \"fix\" things or \"recover,\" i'm just signing up for another decade of this same crushing weight. it's like there's no actual way to find peace without just... giving up everything. do you think it's even possible to actually find rest when everything is this broken?",
